## Installation Options

### 1. uvx (Easiest)

No installation needed:

```bash
uvx specfact plan init
```

### 2. pip

Install globally:

```bash
pip install specfact-cli
specfact --help
```

### 3. Docker

Run in a container:

```bash
docker run ghcr.io/nold-ai/specfact-cli:latest --help
```

